      "span_text": "ILC3s express cKit. 21 ILC3s expressing CD56 were defined as NCR+ ILC3s (NKp46), approximately half of which express CD56, while CD56-negative ILC3s were considered to be either LTi cells or the half of NCR+ ILC3s that do not express CD56. 21 For the purposes of this paper, these cKit-positive/CD56-negative ILC3s will be referred to as CD56 neg ILC3s."
